Acme-EvilLicense

This module is created for demonstration purposes for a presentation at the
GoOpen 2011 conference.

The module provides some kick-ass functionality solving world's greatest
problems, but the license terms are unreasonable and completely unexpected,
though valid.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Acme::EvilLicense


